reviewText: Need more Latin Dimes DVD productions it incorporates the dancing and interviewing of beautiful, sexy women without sexual content of x-rating. A good balance.

This is a music/model video DVD... If you don't have high expectations, you won't be disappointed. No nudity, no seriously distracting camera effects, the video editing isn't horrible. This is much better than Latin Dimes Reggaeton volume 1. However, hip hop is not my preferred musical genre. But this is ok. And it doesn't cost much.
